---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Bulk Stevia Powder Supplier | 90-99% Stevioside, Rebaudioside A | Weiyijie Bio"
  description="High-quality bulk stevia powder supplier. 90-99% stevioside/rebaudioside A, natural zero-calorie sweetener, food grade, complete certifications, 1kg MOQ, fast delivery."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Stevia Powder (Stevia Extract)</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">High-purity natural zero-calorie stevia sweetener for food, beverage, and dietary supplement applications. Multiple specifications available, complete certifications, 1kg MOQ.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Product Specifications</h2>
            <table class="w-full">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Product Name</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Stevia Extract (Stevia Rebaudiana Extract)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Active Ingredients</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Stevioside, Rebaudioside A (Reb A), Rebaudioside D, Rebaudioside M</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Available Purity</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">
                  • Stevioside: 90%, 95%, 98%<br>
                  • Rebaudioside A: 60%, 80%, 97%, 99%<br>
                  • Rebaudioside D/M: 90%+<br>
                  • Blended formulations for specific taste profiles
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Appearance</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">White or light yellow fine powder</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">CAS Number</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">57817-89-7 (Stevioside)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Sweetness</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">200-450x sweeter than sucrose</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Solubility</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Highly soluble in water and ethanol, stable under heat and wide pH range (3-10)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Calorie Content</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">0 kcal/g, zero glycemic index</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Key Benefits</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🍬</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Zero calories:</strong> Perfect for sugar-free, low-carb, and keto products, does not affect blood sugar levels</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🦷</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Tooth-friendly:</strong> Non-cariogenic, does not cause tooth decay, ideal for oral care products and sugar-free confectionery</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Health benefits:</strong> May help lower blood pressure and blood sugar levels, suitable for diabetics and health-conscious consumers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🌡️</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>High stability:</strong> Heat stable up to 200°C, stable in pH 3-10, long shelf life of 24 months, suitable for all food processing applications</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">✅</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Regulatory approval:</strong> GRAS approved by FDA, EFSA approved in EU, JECFA approved, accepted in over 100 countries worldwide</span>
            </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Applications</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🥤</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Beverages</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Soft drinks, carbonated drinks, juice, flavored water, sports drinks, energy drinks, tea, coffee, and alcoholic beverages. Replacement for sugar and artificial sweeteners.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🍫</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Confectionery</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sugar-free candy, chocolate, chewing gum, mints, gummies, jellies, and frozen desserts. Provides sweet taste without calories.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🍞</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Baked Goods</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Bread, cookies, cakes, pastries, muffins, and cereal bars. Heat stable, maintains sweetness during baking process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">💊</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dietary Supplements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Protein powders, meal replacements, vitamin supplements, weight management products, and diabetic foods. Zero calorie, zero glycemic impact.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🥣</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dairy Products</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yogurt, ice cream, milk drinks, cheese, and dairy desserts. Works well in both cultured and UHT processed products.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🧴</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Oral Care & Cosmetics</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Toothpaste, mouthwash, lip balm, and flavored cosmetic products. Non-cariogenic, does not promote tooth decay.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Packaging & Pricing</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Packaging Options</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>1kg/aluminum foil bag, vacuum sealed, food grade</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>25kg/fiber drum or carton, double plastic bag inside</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🎁</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Custom packaging available (private label, custom sizes, custom blends according to your taste requirements)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Pricing (FOB China, Food Grade)</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Stevioside 90%: $15-$25/kg (depending on order quantity)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Rebaudioside A 97%: $40-$60/kg</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Custom blends: Contact us for quotation</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2">Significant discounts for 1000kg+ orders. Contact us for customized blends and taste optimization services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-200 mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Why Buy Stevia Powder from Weiyijie Bio?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">High quality stevia leaves sourced from pollution-free plantations in Yunnan, China, no pesticides or heavy metals</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Advanced extraction technology minimizes bitter aftertaste, clean sweet taste profile</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Multiple specifications available, custom taste blending service to match your product requirements</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Complete certifications: COA, SDS, TDS, FDA GRAS, EFSA approved, Kosher/Halal/Organic certified</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">1kg MOQ, sample orders available for taste testing and formulation trials</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Fast delivery: 3-5 days for stock, 7-15 days global shipping, door-to-door delivery available</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Free technical support for product formulation and dosage recommendations</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all mr-4">
            Request Free Sample
          </a>
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-white border-2 border-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 text-green-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
            Get Bulk Quote Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
